blogPost.excerpt: We’re back in the bathroom for another very fun episode! Today I’m joined by the hilarious and lovely host of Call Her Daddy, Alex “The Father” Cooper. Watch as we reminiscence on our time living in New York (with bagels, of course), discuss female empowerment and how Call Her Daddy has evolved over the years, and play a very fun game of Heads Up!

Senate President Steve Sweeney could be the most potentially shocking upset from the general election, but he’s not the only Democratic legislator in trouble. In the lower half of his ticket, Democratic Assemblymen John Burzichelli and Adam Taliaferro could both lose. Upsets are also looming in other districts.
